---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Cookie policy | StartMonday.AI">
  <section class="container-content py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="mt-4">Cookie policy</h1>
    <div class="prose-brand mt-10">
      <p>We use a small number of cookies to make the site work and — with your permission — to understand how it's used. No non-essential cookies are set until you give consent.</p>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Categories</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Strictly necessary</strong> — required for the site to function (e.g. language preference).</li>
        <li><strong>Functional</strong> — remember preferences and improve experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — aggregate, privacy-respecting usage statistics.</li>
        <li><strong>Marketing</strong> — only if we ever run campaigns; currently none.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Cookies in use</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>sm_cookie_choice</strong> — Stores your cookie preference. Duration: 12 months. Category: necessary.</li>
        <li><strong>Plausible script cookies</strong> — none by default for basic analytics mode. Category: analytics (consent required).</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-ink mt-8">Managing consent</h3>
      <p>Use the consent banner shown on your first visit. You can clear your browser storage to show the banner again.</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-graphite/70">Last updated: 2026-04-30</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
